<Author>rka329
<Content>Fine stay at the Ocean View After reading these reviews we were not sure what we were going to find at the Vieques Ocean View Hotel, but our stay was more than fine. The hotel staff were friendly, and the hotel was conveniently located near the ferry dock in Isabel Segunda. The room was clean and a good size, with a door that opened onto a sunny large shared balcony. The bathroom was a little older, but for the price, it was completely fine. Vieques hotels seemed to be pretty pricey, and this was one of the cheaper places, and it was what we expected: No frills, but clean and fine. Also, It was nice that a cooked-to-order breakfast was included in the room price. 
